data.description: Beautiful 2 story home nestled in the popular Siena neighborhood! Upon entering, you are greeted with an open concept foyer and a grand staircase. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, light granite countertops with honey brown finished cabinets an oversized center island and a breakfast bar! The spacious primary bedroom is located on the main level with an en-suite consisting of a double vanity, separate walk-in shower, relaxing soaking tub and a large walk-in closet. Upstairs you will find a second family room and 3 additional bedrooms. Covered patio and a huge fenced in backyard. Nice landscaping, trees and a small shed! With amenities such 2 pools, 2 basketball courts, volleyball courts, soccer fields and tennis courts.  Walking trails and a community center that serves all! Fun for the whole family! Veterans Memorial School is minutes away. Located minutes from the community clubhouse, playground, and pool. Less than fifteen minutes from Kalahari Waterpark and the new Samsung center in Taylor, TX.  Don't miss this opportunity!
